          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "While Farley took first in his class in Group 6 on Saturday, he had to settle for second overall. Scott Borchetta, a music industry mogul from Nashville, took first overall with his 1969 Chevrolet Corvette. Thus, the Cobra vs Corvette rivalry continues today.",
