            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". The concern is that the CEO will be seriously injured or killed while driving around the track. Wallstreet types are inherently skittish and must be a lot of fun at parties. What really puts the icing on the cake is that Farley went racing after Ford’s first-quarter earnings report dropped, which exceeded investor expectations.",
