          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Previously, Farley has shown off his 1978 Lola T298 and 1966 Ford GT40 on the track. The man has participated in all kinds of races, like the Spa Six Hours and Le Mans Classic. Now it seems he’s added another classic ",
